  "text": "For the method linearity, the procedure was the same as that of system linearity, but the sample was a solution containing the PLGA nanoparticles (placebo) and adding an increased amount of CB13, dissolved in the medium. The results were treated the same way for the system linearity [CITATION_1] .",
